#

Savory Cheddar and Chive Waffles

25 min
$8.5
300 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

DairyGluten

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianNut-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Breakfast

Tags:

BrunchComfort FoodEasy Recipes

Description

Deliciously fluffy waffles infused with sharp cheddar and fresh chives, perfect for breakfast or brunch!

Ingredients

  • all-purpose flour: 1 cup
  • baking powder: 2 tsp
  • salt: 1/2 tsp
  • milk: 1 cup
  • eggs: 1
  • shredded cheddar cheese: 1 cup
  • chopped chives: 1/4 cup
  • butter, melted: 2 tbsp
  • olive oil: 1 tbsp
